1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,900
=Episode 15=

23
00:01:45,299 --> 00:01:47,099
Before I left Jinxin,

24
00:01:47,099 --> 00:01:49,220
we never had overtime on this scale.

25
00:01:49,627 --> 00:01:50,466
Zhuang Shanshan,

26
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:52,500
so many people
are cleaning up your mess.

27
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:53,635
Aren't you ashamed?

28
00:01:54,860 --> 00:01:56,299
Wow.

29
00:01:56,962 --> 00:01:58,207
What time is it?

30
00:01:58,207 --> 00:01:59,459
You're still working?

31
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:01,860
If you can't stand it at Jinxin,

32
00:02:01,860 --> 00:02:03,060
come to Guolong.

33
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:04,459
My doors are wide open.

34
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:06,620
Poaching right at someone else's doorstep?

35
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:07,780
Have you no shame?

36
00:02:09,099 --> 00:02:10,900
Shame? Says the one
who makes expired food.

37
00:02:10,962 --> 00:02:12,220
I'm not arguing with you today.

38
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:13,940
Zhuang Shanshan,

39
00:02:14,087 --> 00:02:15,327
a bet is a bet.

40
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,991
I keep my word.

41
00:02:19,337 --> 00:02:20,419
I'll leave on my own.

42
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:21,900
But this

43
00:02:22,139 --> 00:02:23,579
has nothing to do with Yan.

44
00:02:24,900 --> 00:02:26,979
That's not what you promised me before.

45
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:29,259
Isn't it a little late
to go back on your word now?

46
00:02:29,259 --> 00:02:32,099
Before Jinxin Food admits fault
and agrees to return the orders,

47
00:02:32,099 --> 00:02:33,460
this competition isn't over.

48
00:02:34,462 --> 00:02:35,142
You!

49
00:02:35,225 --> 00:02:36,024
Look.

50
00:02:36,962 --> 00:02:40,282
Jinxin won't have an easy time
solving this mess, right?

51
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:41,739
For businesspeople,

52
00:02:41,739 --> 00:02:43,300
time is everything.

53
00:02:43,450 --> 00:02:44,849
How about we both take a step back?

54
00:02:45,537 --> 00:02:47,690
Let Jiamin transfer her shares
to Zhang Guolong.

55
00:02:48,100 --> 00:02:50,220
Once we get the money, we're done.

56
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,300
You'll have more time

57
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:54,060
to deal with this crisis.

58
00:02:54,220 --> 00:02:55,579
Dream on.

59
00:02:55,859 --> 00:02:56,175
Jiamin,

60
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:58,220
I know you've never liked me.

61
00:02:58,925 --> 00:03:00,699
But I hope you won't
make the wrong decision

62
00:03:00,699 --> 00:03:01,699
just because you hate me.

63
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:03,659
Fine.

64
00:03:03,659 --> 00:03:05,825
If you publish a public notice

65
00:03:05,825 --> 00:03:07,060
admitting you seduced Zeyang,

66
00:03:07,259 --> 00:03:09,587
I might reconsider signing
the transfer agreement.

67
00:03:09,859 --> 00:03:11,259
That's enough, Qin Jiamin.

68
00:03:11,579 --> 00:03:13,699
Shanshan was with Zhou Zeyang first.

69
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,699
We didn't make a scene
when you hooked up with that jerk,

70
00:03:15,699 --> 00:03:17,050
and you still won't give it a rest?

71
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:18,139
Public notice?

72
00:03:18,139 --> 00:03:19,579
As if we would.

73
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:21,699
Fine, I agree.

74
00:03:23,859 --> 00:03:24,620
It's alright, Yan.

75
00:03:24,987 --> 00:03:26,348
As long as we can save Jinxin,

76
00:03:26,348 --> 00:03:27,588
a newspaper notice is nothing.

77
00:03:27,725 --> 00:03:28,686
I'll do it.

78
00:03:29,220 --> 00:03:30,430
You're not publishing anything.

79
00:03:32,937 --> 00:03:34,180
Who was behind the expired food?

80
00:03:34,180 --> 00:03:35,740
Don't you know very well?

81
00:03:36,660 --> 00:03:38,500
We've found out
there's a mole in the company.

82
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:39,940
The police are already investigating.

83
00:03:39,979 --> 00:03:41,020
Before the truth comes out,

84
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,379
no one is transferring any shares.

85
00:03:45,259 --> 00:03:46,139
Qin Jiamin,

86
00:03:46,259 --> 00:03:47,312
you think I'm an idiot?

87
00:03:47,475 --> 00:03:48,755
You never told me about this.

88
00:03:48,755 --> 00:03:50,740
You said from the start that
the shares would be transferred to me.

89
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:52,300
Otherwise, I wouldn't have wasted time

90
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,740
on your stupid family drama.

91
00:03:53,740 --> 00:03:55,099
Listen, Qin Jiamin.

92
00:03:55,099 --> 00:03:57,300
You're signing today,
whether you like it or not.

93
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:57,859
Let's go.

94
00:03:59,340 --> 00:03:59,740
Long.

95
00:03:59,859 --> 00:04:00,460
Get lost.

96
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:01,139
Let's go.

97
00:04:01,340 --> 00:04:01,819
I...

98
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:04,499
Long.

99
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:08,340
Hit me again? Get them!

100
00:04:12,775 --> 00:04:13,340
Shanshan!

101
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:17,339
Minor fracture.

102
00:04:17,579 --> 00:04:18,940
If you still want to keep dancing,

103
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:21,550
I suggest you stay in the hospital
for observation for a few days.

104
00:04:23,670 --> 00:04:24,420
Thank you, doctor.

105
00:04:24,620 --> 00:04:25,139
It's alright.

106
00:04:30,660 --> 00:04:31,660
Yan,

107
00:04:33,339 --> 00:04:34,459
don't worry.

108
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:35,300
Qin Mo,

109
00:04:35,579 --> 00:04:37,219
please take care of Shanshan.

110
00:04:38,379 --> 00:04:39,699
I need to go out for a bit.

111
00:04:44,339 --> 00:04:45,100
Brother Qin,

112
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:46,860
I'm fine.

113
00:04:47,019 --> 00:04:48,259
Go check on Yan.

114
00:04:48,860 --> 00:04:49,420
Alright.

115
00:04:57,540 --> 00:04:58,180
Zhuang Yan,

116
00:04:58,779 --> 00:05:00,300
even if Zhang Guolong deserves it,

117
00:05:00,819 --> 00:05:02,980
you can't solve anything by going alone.

118
00:05:04,620 --> 00:05:06,819
Do you think I'm going
to settle scores with him?

119
00:05:07,779 --> 00:05:09,699
Am I brainless or what?

120
00:05:12,579 --> 00:05:14,019
Where are you going?

121
00:05:15,019 --> 00:05:17,660
I'm heading back to the office
to look into the expired food issue.

122
00:05:19,379 --> 00:05:21,379
I can't let Shanshan take the blame
for nothing.

123
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,899
I wanted Zhang Guolong to be arrested,

124
00:05:24,899 --> 00:05:26,100
just like fate intended.

125
00:05:27,019 --> 00:05:28,300
But since he's asking for death,

126
00:05:28,379 --> 00:05:29,339
I'll give him a push.

127
00:05:31,019 --> 00:05:31,660
Zhuang Yan,

128
00:05:32,579 --> 00:05:33,980
if you trust me,

129
00:05:34,699 --> 00:05:35,860
leave this to me.

130
00:05:36,575 --> 00:05:38,500
(New Beginning Billiards Hall)

131
00:05:42,259 --> 00:05:43,379
Miss,

132
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:45,940
please forgive me, okay?

133
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:49,420
I just wanted to scare them.

134
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:51,660
How could I really hurt you?

135
00:05:52,312 --> 00:05:52,993
Look,

136
00:05:52,993 --> 00:05:54,873
we agreed before.

137
00:05:55,139 --> 00:05:56,540
I've done what I was supposed to.

138
00:05:56,975 --> 00:05:58,975
So just sign the contract.

139
00:05:58,975 --> 00:06:00,415
Do you think I'm stupid?

140
00:06:00,487 --> 00:06:01,367
If not for my brother,

141
00:06:01,367 --> 00:06:03,180
I'd be the one injured right now.

142
00:06:03,180 --> 00:06:04,579
No.

143
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,199
Jiamin,

144
00:06:06,699 --> 00:06:08,620
Mr. Zhang just acted on impulse.

145
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,400
If your brother really cared about you,

146
00:06:10,660 --> 00:06:12,217
why would he throw you out of the house?

147
00:06:12,375 --> 00:06:14,094
But even if I sign, it's useless.

148
00:06:14,212 --> 00:06:16,660
Doesn't it need the shareholders' vote?

149
00:06:17,459 --> 00:06:20,339
That's between Mr. Zhang and Qin Mo.

150
00:06:20,339 --> 00:06:21,060
Right.

151
00:06:21,060 --> 00:06:22,459
That has nothing to do with us.

152
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:25,259
Stop thinking about him so much.

153
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:27,030
You always treat him
as your closest family.

154
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,860
What about him?

155
00:06:28,819 --> 00:06:30,579
He's long since forgotten all about you.

156
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:32,620
Exactly.

157
00:07:03,699 --> 00:07:04,300
Boss!

158
00:07:06,860 --> 00:07:07,540
What?

159
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,100
This is bad!

160
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:09,740
What did I teach you?

161
00:07:10,139 --> 00:07:12,259
Always be steady.

162
00:07:12,259 --> 00:07:14,540
The gutter oil operation at the factory
has been busted.

163
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:15,779
What?

164
00:07:17,459 --> 00:07:18,779
Who tipped them off? Who?

165
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:21,500
Mr. Zhang,

166
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:23,579
you really are full of surprises.

167
00:07:23,580 --> 00:07:24,990
Looks like the contract can't be signed.

168
00:07:25,259 --> 00:07:26,579
Even if the shareholders agree,

169
00:07:26,819 --> 00:07:27,899
I won't hand Jinxin over

170
00:07:27,899 --> 00:07:29,779
to a criminal
who's about to go to prison.

171
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:31,300
Zeyang, let's leave.

172
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:35,500
Get over here.

173
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,779
Have you lost your mind?

174
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:38,339
Mr. Zhang.

175
00:07:38,339 --> 00:07:38,987
Stay still.

176
00:07:39,420 --> 00:07:40,899
I've got nothing left to lose.

177
00:07:40,899 --> 00:07:41,779
Trying to run?

178
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,860
In your dreams.

179
00:07:42,860 --> 00:07:43,779
Mr. Zhang.

180
00:07:43,779 --> 00:07:44,899
Calm down.

181
00:07:44,980 --> 00:07:46,899
Let Jiamin go. Take me as the hostage.

182
00:07:47,379 --> 00:07:48,940
Get lost.

183
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:51,540
Is your life worth anything?

184
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:54,899
You'd better behave.

185
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:56,660
As long as I've got you,

186
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,620
I still have hope.

187
00:08:22,019 --> 00:08:23,880
Police received a tip
from a concerned citizen.

188
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:26,339
Guolong Food factory was using
gutter oil to process food.

189
00:08:26,699 --> 00:08:28,060
The tip has been verified.

190
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:30,700
Police have seized a large number
of gutter oil production lines.

191
00:08:30,899 --> 00:08:32,900
Fifty-six people
are involved in the crime.

192
00:08:33,339 --> 00:08:36,219
The main culprit, Zhang Guolong,
is currently at large.

193
00:08:38,459 --> 00:08:39,979
Zhang Guolong's gutter oil scandal

194
00:08:39,979 --> 00:08:41,699
was exposed this early?

195
00:08:42,339 --> 00:08:43,499
Heaven's on my side.

196
00:08:44,380 --> 00:08:46,579
He also smuggles rare animals.

197
00:08:46,579 --> 00:08:47,990
That's enough to keep him in prison
for life.

198
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:49,859
Concerned citizen?

199
00:08:53,499 --> 00:08:56,819
Mr. Qin, the concerned citizen,
can you tell me

200
00:08:57,099 --> 00:08:59,339
how you knew he was using gutter oil?

201
00:09:00,260 --> 00:09:01,859
Were you in a gang before?

202
00:09:02,499 --> 00:09:03,540
Some kind of mob boss?

203
00:09:04,459 --> 00:09:05,900
Have you watched too many cop movies

204
00:09:05,900 --> 00:09:07,339
and gone stupid?

205
00:09:07,579 --> 00:09:08,739
I run a legitimate business.

206
00:09:09,619 --> 00:09:11,619
But it's hard to avoid dealing
with shady people.

207
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,499
Zhang Guolong has done plenty of evil.

208
00:09:13,699 --> 00:09:15,660
It's not hard to find dirt on him.

209
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:17,699
So you had a way all along

210
00:09:17,699 --> 00:09:18,660
and didn't tell me?

211
00:09:18,660 --> 00:09:19,900
You made me worry for nothing.

212
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:26,540
Are you worried about Zhang Guolong,

213
00:09:27,459 --> 00:09:30,020
or about Mr. Qin, the concerned citizen?

214
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:34,459
Can those even be compared?

215
00:09:34,579 --> 00:09:35,660
Maybe you should think about

216
00:09:35,819 --> 00:09:37,459
what kind of comparison you're making.

217
00:09:37,979 --> 00:09:39,060
Breaking news.

218
00:09:39,110 --> 00:09:41,420
The hiding place of suspect Zhang Guolong
has been exposed.

219
00:09:41,699 --> 00:09:43,380
A young woman surnamed Qin

220
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:44,579
has been taken hostage by him.

221
00:09:45,979 --> 00:09:47,819
- Qin?
- Jiamin.

222
00:09:56,859 --> 00:09:58,499
Stop staring at me.

223
00:09:59,380 --> 00:10:00,180
Keep staring,

224
00:10:01,699 --> 00:10:03,619
or I'll gouge your eyes out.

225
00:10:07,619 --> 00:10:09,459
If I find out who reported me

226
00:10:11,260 --> 00:10:14,619
and betrayed me,

227
00:10:15,219 --> 00:10:16,940
I'll wipe out their whole family!

228
00:10:16,940 --> 00:10:17,739
Boss,

229
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:20,380
the police have started a manhunt.

230
00:10:22,140 --> 00:10:23,499
What are you carrying?

231
00:10:23,979 --> 00:10:24,940
Zhou Zeyang sent this.

232
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,459
He's outside right now.

233
00:10:26,979 --> 00:10:27,819
Open it.

234
00:10:28,579 --> 00:10:29,140
Okay.

235
00:11:09,859 --> 00:11:11,540
Qin Jiamin,

236
00:11:12,780 --> 00:11:15,699
lucky you.

237
00:11:17,459 --> 00:11:19,060
You met such a lovesick fool.

238
00:11:21,819 --> 00:11:23,060
Bring him in.

239
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:27,579
Zeyang!

240
00:11:28,099 --> 00:11:28,699
Jiamin!

241
00:11:29,260 --> 00:11:30,020
Jiamin.

242
00:11:30,859 --> 00:11:32,180
I'm so sorry.

243
00:11:32,180 --> 00:11:33,020
I came too late.

244
00:11:33,499 --> 00:11:35,137
You've suffered, Jiamin.

245
00:11:38,060 --> 00:11:38,699
Mr. Zhang.

246
00:11:39,099 --> 00:11:39,940
Mr. Zhang,

247
00:11:40,739 --> 00:11:42,180
this is all I have.

248
00:11:42,180 --> 00:11:43,130
I'll give it all to you.

249
00:11:43,140 --> 00:11:43,859
Everything.

250
00:11:44,619 --> 00:11:46,060
Please let Jiamin go.

251
00:11:47,619 --> 00:11:49,940
Zeyang, get up.

252
00:11:50,380 --> 00:11:51,140
I'm begging you.

253
00:11:51,780 --> 00:11:52,619
Please.

254
00:11:54,660 --> 00:11:55,300
Jiamin.

255
00:11:57,819 --> 00:11:59,300
Let's go. Don't be scared.

256
00:12:02,020 --> 00:12:03,780
Don't be scared. Let's go.

257
00:12:05,380 --> 00:12:06,180
I'm here.

258
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:26,900
Jiamin,

259
00:12:27,619 --> 00:12:28,380
are you okay?

260
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:29,540
What are you doing here?

261
00:12:31,770 --> 00:12:32,819
Of course I came for you.

262
00:12:33,859 --> 00:12:34,579
Don't worry.

263
00:12:34,780 --> 00:12:36,180
I'll deal with Zhang Guolong.

264
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,260
Come home with me first.

265
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:38,020
Deal with him?

266
00:12:38,339 --> 00:12:39,339
Go home?

267
00:12:39,410 --> 00:12:41,380
Did you forget you were the one
who drove me away?

268
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,660
Where were you
when I was kidnapped by Zhang Guolong?

269
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:46,020
Where were you when I was terrified?

270
00:12:46,579 --> 00:12:47,940
Where were you

271
00:12:47,940 --> 00:12:50,660
when Zeyang gave up everything for me
and knelt to beg Zhang Guolong?

272
00:12:50,900 --> 00:12:51,699
Jiamin,

273
00:12:52,300 --> 00:12:53,499
I'm sorry.

274
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:56,540
I didn't expect Zhang Guolong
to be this insane.

275
00:12:57,780 --> 00:12:58,699
My bad.

276
00:12:59,140 --> 00:13:00,575
Hate me or blame me if you want.

277
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,520
But come home with me first, okay?

278
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:05,180
Qin Mo, you were the one
who didn't want me first.

279
00:13:05,300 --> 00:13:06,260
From today on,

280
00:13:06,260 --> 00:13:07,180
I have no brother

281
00:13:07,180 --> 00:13:08,300
and no family.

282
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:10,180
The only person I care about is Zeyang.

283
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:17,020
Let go of me.

284
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:18,060
- Let go!
- Qin Mo.

285
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:19,060
Jiamin doesn't want to go with you.

286
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:19,900
You can't force her.

287
00:13:22,180 --> 00:13:22,900
Zhou Zeyang,

288
00:13:23,300 --> 00:13:24,339
drop your pretense.

289
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:26,099
Jiamin is my sister.

290
00:13:26,310 --> 00:13:29,390
You know better than anyone how she ended
up being kidnapped by Zhang Guolong.

291
00:13:30,859 --> 00:13:31,979
Let go of me!

292
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:32,940
Zeyang!

293
00:13:33,739 --> 00:13:34,540
Let's go.

294
00:13:53,437 --> 00:13:57,075
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

295
00:13:57,200 --> 00:14:00,512
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

296
00:14:00,675 --> 00:14:04,262
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

297
00:14:04,562 --> 00:14:07,850
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

298
00:14:08,075 --> 00:14:11,700
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

299
00:14:11,862 --> 00:14:15,200
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

300
00:14:15,275 --> 00:14:18,987
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

301
00:14:19,037 --> 00:14:22,900
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

302
00:14:22,962 --> 00:14:29,012
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

303
00:14:30,187 --> 00:14:36,925
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

304
00:14:37,212 --> 00:14:41,487
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

305
00:14:41,487 --> 00:14:44,787
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

306
00:14:44,862 --> 00:14:49,162
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

307
00:14:49,225 --> 00:14:52,875
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

308
00:14:52,875 --> 00:14:56,437
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

309
00:14:56,487 --> 00:14:59,750
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

310
00:14:59,750 --> 00:15:03,500
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

311
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:10,212
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
